metadata.name: Agniskhana
metadata.description:
Eyes are the mirror of the soul. Where words are restrained, the eyes often talk a great deal.
In the photograph, I call the girl as Agnikshana-where Agni and ikshana are two Sanskrit words which defines Fire or fiery eyes.
While I was taking the shot, her eyes were manifesting a charismatic and draconian glimpse to me.
I felt she wore her truth and fire of love in her eyes. The beauty & grace could be seen in her enchanting eyes leading to her heart where love resides.

Photographed by: Arun Hegden
Format: Jpg
Edition: 1/1
Dimensions: 3732x5557
